{"tid":1724474,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[中大二戰支線] 打算係自己區開花救中大既人請留意唔好落單","createTime":"2019-11-15T13:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T13:13:46.000Z","uid":130797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"567d656d2bff989a683a66d19233b330ee49ebd2","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"中大形勢突然緊張<br />\n各位手足一定係好撚擔心想快手落樓幫手係自己區開花<br />\n呢一招唔係咩新招<br />\n班狗都一定會諗到我地咁做<br />\n<br />\n而呢兩日政府安排返左堆黑社會軍隊出黎搞事<br />\n所以手足落樓個陣唔可以太過充昏頭腦<br />\n一定要小心自己既安全 盡量唔好落單<br />\n女手足就更加要小心<br />\n<br />\n各位武運昌隆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e0aa3243760eb2ea734587443c07647ebd5a25","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"推呀!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bf4217b5d39d8358f0d1737090e95b1719da4d","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"推呀!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef22516a02c9a71c9fdd63028075835a811fe5ac","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"推呀!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a22484e9f92a6310037e5299fe011c9ed58809","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n手足要加強自己對環境既注意力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0b197f9ebc3f11f23603c506209785626161e5","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"推多幾野就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a72f8275aa3c5151fd8a67e5aa65ef89a31c0d","tid":1724474,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"